WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.006 --> 00:00:08.383
<i>[Cormac] Previously on</i>
The Continental...

2
00:00:08.384 --> 00:00:10.531
<i>What Frankie took
is very important.</i>

3
00:00:10.532 --> 00:00:12.679
Find your brother.
'cause if you don't.

4
00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:14.682
I'll bring the weight of this
whole institution

5
00:00:14.683 --> 00:00:15.912
down on you both.

6
00:00:15.913 --> 00:00:17.143
[alarm blares]

7
00:00:20.062 --> 00:00:21.480
