<i>[♪ The Funkees: "Ole"]</i>

1136
00:56:24.632 --> 00:56:27.635
<i>[person singing in Igbo]</i>

1137
00:56:27.636 --> 00:56:34.635
<i>♪ ♪</i>

1138
00:57:14.890 --> 00:57:17.517
