- My brother.

1139
00:57:17.518 --> 00:57:18.894
- [Jamal] How you doing. man?
- [Charon] I'm good.

1140
00:57:18.895 --> 00:57:21.188
- [Jamal] Any requests?
- Surprise me.

1141
00:57:21.189 --> 00:57:23.315
Ah. right on. brother.
Right on.

1142
00:57:23.316 --> 00:57:30.315
♪ ♪

1143
00:57:30.322 --> 00:57:33.200
[music stops.
indistinct chatter]

1144
00:57:35.244 --> 00:57:38.247
