1145
00:57:38.248 --> 00:57:43.293
♪ ♪

1146
00:57:43.294 --> 00:57:45.879
<i>[singer]
♪ Nassau's gone funky ♪</i>

1147
00:57:45.880 --> 00:57:48.465
<i>♪ Nassau's gone soul ♪</i>

1148
00:57:48.466 --> 00:57:51.467
♪ ♪

1149
00:57:51.468 --> 00:57:54.137
<i>♪ We've got
a doggone beat now ♪</i>

1150
00:57:54.138 --> 00:57:57.808
<i>♪ We're gonna call
our very own ♪</i>

1151
00:57:57.809 --> 00:58:01.102
Charon? You good?

1152
00:58:01.103 --> 00:58:04.147
Yes. Thank you. Jamal.

1153
00:58:04.148 --> 00:58:06.901
I have no idea
what to write in response.

1154
00:58:06.902 --> 00:58:08.360
Words fail me.

1155
00:58:08.361 --> 00:58:11.404
