<i>♪ Funky Nassau ♪</i>

1178
00:59:16.804 --> 00:59:19.014
<i>♪ Listen. listen good ♪</i>

1179
00:59:19.015 --> 00:59:20.807
<i>♪ ♪</i>

1180
00:59:20.808 --> 00:59:23.017
<i>♪ New York. you know ♪</i>

1181
00:59:23.018 --> 00:59:26.438
<i>♪ Has got
a whole lot of soul ♪</i>

1182
00:59:26.439 --> 00:59:28.439
<i>♪ Good God ♪</i>

1183
00:59:28.440 --> 00:59:31.025
<i>♪ London Town ♪</i>

1184
00:59:31.026 --> 00:59:35.030
<i>♪ Is too doggone cold ♪</i>

1185
00:59:35.031 --> 00:59:36.698
<i>♪ Yeah ♪</i>

1186
