1206
01:00:25.372 --> 01:00:26.914
Come here. you little shit!

1207
01:00:26.915 --> 01:00:28.667
Why you keep breaking
my windows. huh?

1208
01:00:28.668 --> 01:00:30.669
Get your hands off him.

1209
